Name: UndTime
Description: Time spent on architectural understanding tasks, in seconds.

Name: UndCorr
Description: Correctness of architectural understanding tasks (e.g. the number of tasks correctly answered).

Name: ModTime
Description: Time spent on impact analysis tasks, in seconds.

Name: ModComp
Description: Completeness of the impact analysis, obtained by dividing the number of correct files informed by the participant by the actual number of correct files. The maximum value is two because there are two impact analysis tasks.

Name: ModCorr
Description: Correctness of the impact analysis, obtained by dividing the number of correct files informed by the participant by the number of files informed by the participant. The maximum value is two because there are two impact analysis tasks.

Name: ModRate
Description: Modification rate, obtained by dividing the number of correct files informed by the participant by ModTime.
